*Svedok* je rekao da je čuo šum u dvorištu. (The witness said he heard noise in the yard.)

Ona je bila *svedok* njegovog čina. (She was a witness to his deed.)

Oni su bili *svedoci* njenog pada. (They were witnesses to her fall.)

On je zatražio *svedoke* da mu pomognu. (He asked for witnesses to help him.)

On je postao *svedokom* njenog uspeha. (He became a witness to her success.)